Fortuna Gains for Second Day on Plan to Start Lottery Earlier

-- B y   K r y s t o f   C h a m o n i k o l a s
-- 
2011-04-06T08:05:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-06/fortuna-gains-for-second-day-on-plan-to-start-lottery-earlier.html
Fortuna Entertainment Group NV (FORTUNA)  rose
for a second day after the Czech bookmaker said yesterday it
will start a lottery three months earlier than planned.  The stock rose 1.4 percent to 109 koruna as of 9:50 a.m. in
 Prague , heading for its highest closing price since the
Amsterdam-registered company began trading in Prague on Oct. 22.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Krystof Chamonikolas in Prague at 
 kchamonikola@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at   gserkin@bloomberg.net  